                        "displayName": "Cristian Bichis",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Thanks Freeaqingme, take your time...",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=avantis",
                        "name": "avantis",
                        "displayName": "Cristian Bichis",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2011-05-26T16:08:49.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2011-05-26T16:08:49.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/46946",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=ganjalatte",
                        "name": "ganjalatte",
                        "displayName": "Marvin Feldmann",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "As mentioned above this patch does not work for chained routes. I patched this issue by comparing the assembled URLs of the current route and the route used by Zend_Navigation_Page_Mvc:\r\n\r\n{code}\r\nif ($this->_route) {\r\n    \/*\r\n     * Patch ZF-11359\r\n     * For Zend_Controller_Router_Route_Chain\r\n     *\/\r\n    try {\r\n        if ($front->getRouter()->getCurrentRouteName() === $this->_route && $this->getHref() === self::$_urlHelper->url(array(), null, false, false)) {\r\n            $this->_active = true;\r\n            return true;\r\n        }\r\n    } catch (Zend_Controller_Router_Exception $e) {\r\n    }\r\n\r\n\r\n    \/**\r\n     * Patch ZF-11359\r\n     * ZF-11359_Fix_Patch.diff\r\n     *\/\r\n    $route = $front->getRouter()->getRoute($this->_route);\r\n    if(method_exists($route, 'getDefaults')) {\r\n        $myParams = array_merge($route->getDefaults(), $myParams);\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n{code}",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=ganjalatte",
                        "name": "ganjalatte",
                        "displayName": "Marvin Feldmann",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2011-06-01T01:53:45.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2011-06-01T01:53:45.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/46958",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=avantis",
                        "name": "avantis",
                        "displayName": "Cristian Bichis",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I guess would worth to check if the route is chained and only use the patch for a chained route.\r\n\r\nThis makes sense to avoid too much assemble processing....",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=avantis",
                        "name": "avantis",
                        "displayName": "Cristian Bichis",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2011-06-02T07:40:01.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2011-06-02T07:40:01.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/46970",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=freak",
                        "name": "freak",
                        "displayName": "Dolf Schimmel (Freeaqingme)",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "This issue was assigned to me because it was about merely applying a patch. Apparently the patch does not meet the quality standards ZF aims at. I am reassigning the issue, and assume it will not be resolved before ZF2.\r\n\r\nOf course, this is not the case if a patch shows up that also supports chained links in a performant manner. Thank you for making ZF better!",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=freak",
                        "name": "freak",
                        "displayName": "Dolf Schimmel (Freeaqingme)",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2011-06-04T00:15:42.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2011-06-04T00:15:42.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/46978",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=avantis",
                        "name": "avantis",
                        "displayName": "Cristian Bichis",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Freeaqingme, i suggest to at least patch with the initial solution, which works for non-chained routes. Otherwise it makes sense to fully remove the isActive related features...\r\n\r\nI mean, there is a solution which is fixing for at least many of the cases so it makes sense to either apply the patch or remove the features (which i don't think is a choice would lead to BC break).",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=avantis",
                        "name": "avantis",
                        "displayName": "Cristian Bichis",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2011-06-04T11:05:16.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2011-06-04T11:05:16.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/46979",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=freak",
                        "name": "freak",
                        "displayName": "Dolf Schimmel (Freeaqingme)",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Applied original patch(es). They should be released with version 1.11.8.\r\n\r\nCommitted in r24118 merged with release 1.11 branch in r24119. For the chained route stuff, please create a new issue.\r\n\r\nThank you for making ZF better.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=freak",
                        "name": "freak",
                        "displayName": "Dolf Schimmel (Freeaqingme)",
